trans-unit.source: Represents the method implemented by the UI Automation client application to handle the event raised by a UI Automation provider when the focus has changed.
trans-unit.target: Representerer metoden implementeres av Brukergrensesnittet Automation klientprogrammet behandle hendelsen utløst av en leverandør av Brukergrensesnittet Automation når fokus er endret.

trans-unit.source: Use an AutomationFocusChangedEventHandler delegate to define the method that is called by a client to handle [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] focus-changed events.
trans-unit.target: Bruk en AutomationFocusChangedEventHandler representant til å definere metoden kalles av en klient til å håndtere [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] fokus endret-hendelser.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> represented by `sender` might not have any cached properties or patterns, depending on whether the application subscribed to this event while a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest> was active.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>representert av `sender` kan ikke ha noen hurtigbufret egenskaper og mønstre, avhengig av om programmet abonnerer på denne hendelsen under en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest>var aktiv.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.CacheRequest> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>
